obe with long sleeves.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\", \"score\": 0.9999921080973219, \"rank\": 7.251619056213806e-06, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the traditional piece\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"an ankle-long asymmetrical robe\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"long sleeves\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vests, which serve as the centerpiece of the outfits, feature a blend of national and Olympic symbols, including theGua Maral(mystical deer),Nine White Banners, and the Olympic torch.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.9793179568037461, \"rank\": 0.021118819689363126, \"text\": \"White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eight_Banners\", \"score\": 0.8984324063385825, \"rank\": 0.11304091093551552, \"text\": \"Banners\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eight_Banners\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eight_Banners\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vests\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"the centerpiece\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"the outfits\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"a blend\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"national and Olympic symbols\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic torch\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are Instagram posts with women and men flag