urce/Qing_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.7521343807335099, \"rank\": 0.27578118272205193, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qing_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qing_dynasty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"alackof creativity\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"andblamedthe label\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"theManchu\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2919}, {\"ngram\": \"an ethnic minority\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The criticism was so overwhelming that the label reacted to it with a video in which one of the founders evencriedin response to the hate from the public.\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 3130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The criticism\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"the label\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3024}, {\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"the founders\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"the hate\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is a post on Facebook criticizing the uniforms' resemblance to the traditional clothing of Manchu people in China.\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3228, \"end\": 3241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchu_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manchu people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchu_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchu_people\"}, {\"begin\": 3245, \"end\": 3250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qing_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.7521343807335099, \"rank\": 0.27578118272205193, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qing_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qing_dynasty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a post\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"Facebook\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3158}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniforms' resemblance\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3196}, {\"ngram\": \"the traditional clothing\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Explanations for the criticism lie in the country's history.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Explanations\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3267}, {\"ngram\": \"the criticism\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's history\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1691, Mongolia came under the control of the Manchu-ledQing Dynastyand remainedsubjugatedto Chinese rule for more than 200 years until declaring independence in 1911.\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3325, \"end\": 3333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9999996220509079, \"rank\": 2.3489868953078086e-07, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 3411, \"end\": 3418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9880588783564117, \"rank\": 0.011280600145325866, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the control\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3356}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 200 years\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3447}, {\"ngram\": \"independence\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This lengthy imperial ruleexploitedMongolia's natural resources, tried to assimilate the local population into Chinese culture, and crushed attempts to regain independence.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3597, \"end\": 3612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_